# Baseline

Every major build must have baseline metrics.

Example:

```text
Build: 0.1.0
Map: BenchmarkWorld
Heroes: 100
Monsters: 500
FPS Avg: 60
FPS Min: 55
Memory: 180 MB
AI Tick: 1.2 ms
Combat Tick: 0.8 ms
Navigation Tick: 2.1 ms
```

Never optimize without a baseline.

